arStrings.szText: "You made a promise to that child. Were you lying?"
I do not know. (chuckles) I hope not.
Ah, you brought the blood, good. I'll begin distilling it immediately. And what’s this? A nangari tooth? Larger than any I’ve seen.
A progenitor. A progenitor who may still live.
You must find her. If the blood you found turns out to be too weak, we should have a more potent sample ready. Just in case.
